data.description: DESTIN LIVING AT IT'S FINEST!  Less than 2 miles from the beach and harbor, a block away from the bay, outdoor living space and heated pool... The list just goes on and on and on!!!  this recently renovated Florida cottage speaks for itself and you will not want to miss scheduling your personal tour of this gem as soon as possible!  The complete renovation done in 2015 by the owner of Destin's iconic AJ's Seafood House in addition to the brand new HVAC, and pool heater make this home an entertainer's dream complete with the gourmet kitchen and cypress live edge wood topped island.  The custom surround sound and all professionally mounted TV's convey.  Do not miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home today!
